text: Tha Doggfather is the second studio album by Snoop Doggy Dogg. This album was released on November 12, 1996. The album sold two million copies. The singles released were "Snoop's Upside Your Head", "Vapors" and "Doggfather" ==References== Category:1996 albums Category:Snoop Dogg albums Category:Death Row Records albums
title: Tha Doggfather
